        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "B−2 Suppose that f : [0, 1] → R has a continuous derivative and that J0 f (x) dx = 0. Prove that for every α ∈ (0, 1),",
        "bbox": [
          0.5231372549019608,
